cu.explanation_en: Setting the integrity algorithm to the unknown enum 'nia9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the ASN.1 verbosity to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing errors and system initialization failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 ASN.1 詳細程度設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致配置解析錯誤，並造成系統初始化失敗。
